HEADWORD: Consular
<hw>Con"su*lar</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>consularis</ets>; cf. F. <ets>consulaire</ets>.]</ety> <def>Of or
pertaining to a consul; performing the duties of a consul; <as>as,
